descriptionHtml:
[size=6][color=#ffd966]Fantasy Male ECE Save Preset[/color] 

[/size][size=4]Two presets. Will work for most humanoid races but tailor-made for Male Imperial. Save Slots 12 and 15. Place in "CME_save" folder.[/size]

Recommended mods:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7887/?]Pretty Face by tktk[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57952/?]Milkdrinker male texture by Fiszi[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11387/?]a bit more feminine faces for males by bezzarnaam[/url] 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55364/?]Kijiko Hair by Kijiko and Goldiocks[/url]

Those who wish to use this for NPC mods, like followers, can go right ahead. No permissions necessary but credit would be appreciated. Backstory on my player character: He be a fantasy version my Skyrim persona - "Aerys the Mad Dovahking" (inspired by [url=http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen]Aerys II Targaryen[/url].)
author: AerysTMD
